Class Project

java.lang.Object
org.gbif.api.model.registry.eml.Project
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Project extends Object implements Serializable
A dataset can be part of a project. A project can have a unique identifier, used to link datasets associated with the same project.
